<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning-box strong {
            color: #856404;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .link-text {
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîí Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>${userName}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>${companyName}</strong> account.</p>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This password reset link will expire in <strong>${expiryTime}</strong>.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
            
            <center>
                <a href="${resetLink}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            </center>
            
            <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p class="link-text">${resetLink}</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è Did not request this?</strong></p>
                <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>For security reasons, never share your password with anyone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at: <a href="mailto:${supportEmail}">${supportEmail}</a></p>
            <p><strong>${companyName}</strong></p>
            <p>¬© 2025 All rights reserved</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
